reviewText: I received this video in just a few days. It is in excellent condition and plays as you would expect. That is about all I think needs to be said about the experience. If I am going to review the content I will leave that on iMDB or Rotten Tomatoes/Flixster.
awesome biker flick. made like 1970's biker movie but with way hotter women.
Absolutely love this movie. It came fast and packaged the way it should. No complaints!
Damn cool movie, reminds me of the classic B Biker movies from the drive-in back in the 60's including the music.  A cool movie to run during a party!
